Assistant HR Manager
DR SULAIMAN AL HABIB MEDICAL CENTER
Location:
Dubai Healthcare City, Dubai
Date: 05-05-2014
Job Type: Contract
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
HR
DR SULAIMAN AL HABIB MEDICAL CENTER
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
Education:Graduate of an accredited college or university in Human Resource Management is essential preferably Master of Business Administration in Human Resource Management
Experience:Minimum Five (5) years experience in medium size business.HOSPITAL EXPERIENCE IS A MUST.
Knowledge/Skills:  Ability to manage time effectively in fast paced environment. Program planning and show great leadership skills, skill in budgeting cost estimating and fiscal management principles and procedures, knowledge of computer systems and applications, strong interpersonal and communication skills and the ability to work effectively with a wide range of constituencies in a diverse community and must have ability to develop, plan and implement short and long term goals.
Language:Fluent in spoken and written English. Spoken Arabic is desirable.
Travel:some travel may be required
